urlText: Minto Station Lift 3 between the footbridge and Platform 2 or Minto Rd is not available
content:
At Minto Station Lift 3 between the footbridge and Platform 2 or Minto Rd is temporarily out of service.
From Friday 21 June to Friday 28 June 2024 inclusive, lift upgrades will be taking place, closing the lift between the concourse and Minto Road. Customers with accessible needs can use the accessible ramp on Minto Road or lift on Somerset Street to enter and exit the station. 
If you need help, ask staff or phone 02 4629 0842.
